name: 2023: Year in Review (Awards, Newlywed Game, Stats)
description:
Watch this video to see the highs and lows of 2023 here at the GreenerGrass YouTube Channel! 

We’re two of the luckiest people in the world and, thanks to you, we’ve been able to share some of our exciting adventures on land, sea, and air here in YouTube! 

In this video, we'll revisit the year we’ve just had. We’ll give out a handful of “awards” highlighting the best (and the worst) of 2021 in all kinds of categories!
